snippet.title: Ghosts 'N' Goblins [Commodore 16 game] (almost longplay :D)
snippet.description: Okay, this version I am playing here is technically called Inferno, but there is like 1% difference to 16k GNG. While checking out this, I discovered a bug with the first level boss that made it easier to reach the second level (which is the last one here). Other than that, the bosses are impossible to get around.
